unittitle_ssm: New York University Library Accession Books
abstract_ssm: The collection contains ledgers recording the accession of books, periodicals, manuscripts, and other items by various New York University libraries between 1830 and 1967. Some ledgers contain catalogs of authors, theses, and bill payments.
